To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Harami _harami;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_harami = Harami(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_harami.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "harami", _harami.Current.Value);
}

symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.harami = self.Harami(symbol)
